{% comment %}
  AayuPain™ Official Refunds & Cancellations Policy Section
{% endcomment %}

<div class="aayu-policy-page-wrapper">
  <div class="page-width page-width--narrow">
    <div class="aayu-policy-header">
      <span class="aayu-policy-badge">HASSLE-FREE GUARANTEE</span>
      <h1 class="aayu-policy-title">Refunds & Cancellations</h1>
      <p class="aayu-policy-date">AyuPain™ Customer Protection Policy | support@ayupain.in</p>
    </div>

    <div class="aayu-policy-content">
      <div class="aayu-policy-card">
        <h2>1. Order Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <p>You can cancel your order free of cost at any time before it is dispatched from our warehouse.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>To cancel an order, please contact our support team immediately via Email (<a href="mailto:support@ayupain.in">support@ayupain.in</a>) or Call/WhatsApp (<a href="tel:8197383570">+91 8197383570</a>).</li>
          <li>Once an order is dispatched and handed over to our courier partner, it cannot be canceled in transit.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="aayu-policy-card">
        <h2>2. 7-Day Replacement & Return Guarantee</h2>
        <p>Your satisfaction is our top priority. We accept returns or replacements within 7 days of delivery under the following conditions:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>The product received is damaged, leaked, defective, or incorrect.</li>
          <li>The seal is broken or tamper-evident packaging was damaged during transit.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><em>Note: Please share a clear unboxing photo or video of the received parcel to expedite your return request.</em></p>
      </div>

      <div class="aayu-policy-card">
        <h2>3. Refund Process & Timelines</h2>
        <p>Once your returned item or proof of damage is verified by our team:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Prepaid Orders (UPI/Card/NetBanking):</strong> Refunds are credited back to your original payment method within 5 to 7 working days.</li>
          <li><strong>Cash on Delivery (COD) Orders:</strong> Refunds will be issued via UPI transfer or direct Bank Transfer to the details provided by the customer within 5 to 7 working days.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="aayu-policy-card">
        <h2>4. How to Initiate a Return or Refund Request</h2>
        <p>To request a return, exchange, or refund, follow these simple steps:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Send an email to <a href="mailto:support@ayupain.in">support@ayupain.in</a> with your Order ID and photo/video of the product.</li>
          <li>Or message us directly on WhatsApp / Call at <a href="tel:8197383570">+91 8197383570</a>.</li>
          <li>Our care executive will guide you through the return pickup or instant replacement process.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .aayu-policy-page-wrapper {
    padding: 40px 0 70px 0;
    background: #f8faf9;
    font-family: 'Poppins', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
  }
  .aayu-policy-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 35px;
  }
  .aayu-policy-badge {
    background: rgba(14, 90, 54, 0.1);
    color: #0e5a36;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .aayu-policy-title {
    color: #093f25;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 12px 0 6px 0;
  }
  .aayu-policy-date {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .aayu-policy-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .aayu-policy-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
  }
  .aayu-policy-card h2 {
    color: #093f25;
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #cca43b;
    display: inline-block;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .aayu-policy-card p {
    color: #374151;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
  }
  .aayu-policy-card ul, .aayu-policy-card ol {
    margin: 10px 0 10px 20px;
    padding: 0;
    color: #374151;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .aayu-policy-card a {
    color: #0e5a36;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>

